{"tid":1320632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：長輩圖反送中 收工男中伏 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-07-15T12:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T12:48:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5650bef063f9b5f8f9eb5e9de5a278405190868b","tid":1320632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190715/20729530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F20729530&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f8c3c3bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F20729530&h=6a2ebc40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190715/20729530</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：長輩圖反送中 收工男中伏 - 李八方<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190715/large/1563120981_e833.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190715%2Flarge%2F1563120981_e833.jpg&h=3797b617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳百牆其實係曲線反送中，獲唔少網民大讚創作有心思。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n早排班網民玩長輩圖反送中玩到出神入化，「感化」唔少藍絲加入支持成立獨立調查委員會查警察。八方發現原來唔少中年人、長者對長輩圖係完全冇抵抗力，只要係長輩圖就一定睇，有連登仔喺網上分享好多長者、阿叔俾黃絲長輩圖吸引嘅相，估唔到網民再發揮創意，搞個扮係藍絲版嘅連儂牆「陳百牆」出嚟，上面貼晒長輩圖，其實內容係曲線反送中反警，點知連「收工男」傅振中中伏，仲喺facebook分享！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190715/large/1563121009_1978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190715%2Flarge%2F1563121009_1978.jpg&h=a1f47570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n植入反送中訊息嘅長輩圖，真係吸引咗唔少長輩駐足觀看，大收成效！<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190715/large/1563121432_bed4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190715%2Flarge%2F1563121432_bed4.jpg&h=ee243f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「收工男」中伏，錯誤分享反送中嘅陳百牆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林子祥阮兆祥躺着中槍<br />\n<br />\n陳百祥堪稱「深藍」藝人，撐送中同撐警形象深入民心，有巿民整咗幅貼滿隱含反送中訊息長輩圖嘅陳百牆，成功吸引一批上咗年紀嘅巿民駐足觀看，再喺WhatsApp群組之間瘋傳，連出名立場極左嘅「收工男」傅振中，都中伏喺facebook分享話：「我哋有陳百牆，阮兆牆，林子牆同黎耀牆，陰氣冇咁重，一定好過佢嗰連儂牆，鬼佬嘢冇好！」<br />\n<br />\n有收工男分享，唔少藍絲朋友都「讚好」，有人讚呢幅陳百牆「正」，有人話「要全港都有」，更有人讚呢幅牆係「以其人之道還以其人之身」，大讚「叻哥好嘢，支持你」似乎藍絲睇嘢，冇睇內容噃，過去鬧出過唔少笑話嘅工聯會立法會議員「醬爆」陸頌雄，可能瀨嘢經驗豐富，今次就心水清，叫一眾藍絲網友「大家睇真啲，全部都是反對派反送中的內容，唔好中計」，先令部份藍絲網友如夢初醒。<br />\n<br />\n對於醬爆呢個溫馨提示，傅振中唔知係咪想死撐，回覆話：「大家記住一點，我寧願市民思想混亂，都不可以被黃屍洗腦！」  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：不滿偏幫警方 荃灣地產舖停播TVB (李八方)"},{"pid":"aaa31a1d65973bc9188a594f85e53962add43b20","tid":1320632,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻大家<br />\n<br />\n［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b46cf521270966c7d99f01f9f2f38d308c17b82f","tid":1320632,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a>"},{"pid":"26243a0c76c2114bf3fe760e0fc3d1d25f4e49f7","tid":1320632,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"真心膠"},{"pid":"05d7e21099ce9d5d6a2881cb48ab60fcb5e3ab91","tid":1320632,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"連登仔十分險惡狡滑"},{"pid":"0a259c9f05bdccfd44b6394ebe0b0ef0bfecdd26","tid":1320632,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持警察！支持監警會！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320279\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320279</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}